item.title: Pantrypreneur Educate Overview
item.description: Type Description Mobile Pantrypreneur Educate is a small-school offline administration system Intent It focuses on helping teachers manage their students. It comes from our own experience as teacher-students: Klock + Query Appraise Jobs From the TESDA training in 2024, we put up the idea that it should do learning outcomes together with info guides and self-checks Models See the individual features Changelog 2022-07: Abandoned Pantry Apprentice to focus on Pantrypreneur Educate.
